                    <div class="tech">#POSTGRESQL</div>
                    <div class="tech">#KNEX</div>
                    <p class="description">
                        DOTS is a simple dot voting app:
                        <ul>
                            <li class="description">create a poll</li>
                            <li class="description">
                                give the poll code to all participants
                            </li>
                            <li class="description">
                                participants navigate to the app
                            </li>
                            <li class="description">
                                participants vote in the poll
                            </li>
                        </ul>
